Duckhorn Wine Gift Trio
List.Description:
This collection combines the three wines from the renowned Duckhorn Wine Company: Goldeneye, seductive Pinot Noir hailing from the cool-climate Anderson Valley; Cabernet Sauvignon from Duckhorn Vineyards, known for its excellent Bordeaux varietals in Napa Valley; and Paraduxx Z Blend, a smooth and lush Zinfandel, Cabernet Sauvignon, and Merlot blend.

Wine Gift Trio Includes:

  • Goldeneye Anderson Valley Pinot Noir
    Excellent structure and acidity, with layered fruit and firm tannins. Sophisticated aromas of star anise, morel mushrooms and toasty oak segue to enticing ripe berry and bittersweet chocolate notes, underscored by hints of black licorice and truffle.

  • Duckhorn Napa Valley Cabernet Sauvignon
    Aromas of ripe currant, spearmint, marzipan and tobacco lead to intense flavors of blackberry and black cherry, all supported by a subtle framework of French oak, which adds nuance, depth and dimension to the finish.

  • Paraduxx Z Blend
    The aromas are complex and inviting, with lifted red fruit elements of raspberry and plum, as well as deeper bramble fruit notes and layers of vanilla, cream, nutmeg and cinnamon. The wine's lush texture is supported by resolved tannins that lead to a full, ripe finish.

    Due to the popularity of this gift, vintages sometimes sell out. Should this happen, we will always substitute with the current vintage.
